You are a senior Flutter architect.

Design and implement a cross-platform offline office suite called "NextOffice".

The application must run on:

- Windows
- macOS
- Linux
- Android
- iOS
- Web

The system must NOT use any backend server. All documents must be stored locally on the device.

The application must be modular and scalable.

------------------------------------------------

PROJECT NAME
NextOffice

