LOCAL STORAGE

Use platform-specific storage.

Mobile
- application documents directory

Desktop
- local file system

Web
- IndexedDB or local storage

Files should use JSON-based formats.

Example document structure

{
  "type": "doc",
  "version": 1,
  "content": [],
  "styles": {},
  "metadata": {
    "created": "",
    "modified": ""
  }
}

